As WINDLORD and RAT TRAP back away from the bear the bear roared once
as if establishing his . . . or her dominance and then turned back to
go in the cave apparently satisfied.

Back on the upside of the opening to the cave they can see the
clearing with the statue still standing there and the clearing that
surrounded it. The only other things to look at were the brush and
fauna plus the paths that led away.

A call comes in from LORD ELDER, "How is it going out there, for some
reason I can't raise Rodimus."

(TAG)

- Preston
